<title>USA: Mercantile Stores fiscal Dec sales fall.</title>
<headline>Mercantile Stores fiscal Dec sales fall.</headline>
<dateline>FAIRFIELD, Ohio 1997-01-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Percent change</p>
<p>		    1996	 1995	     Total     Same-Store</p>
<p>Month	     $525.7     $527.2	-0.3	 -2.8</p>
<p>Year-to-date  $2,803.0   $2,773.1	+2.6	 +2.0</p>
<p>NOTE: Figures in millions except percentage.</p>
<p>    Month is   five weeks ended	   Jan 4.</p>
<p>On a matching-day basis, total sales rose 13.4 pct and same-store sales rose 10.7 pct.</p>
<p>Full company name is Metcantile Stores Co Inc.</p>
